\h Jesus save me!
\ipi God has already proved His love for you personally. For God so loved the world, that he gave his only begotten Son, that whosoever believeth in him should not perish, but have everlasting life..\vp(John 3:16)\vp*
\ipi Do you believe the Word of Him who created you, who knows you and loves you?
\ipi Are you ready to receive Him, that is, the Word of God - Jesus Christ, through whom all things were made?
\ipi But now commandeth all men every where to repent.\vp(Acts 17:30)\vp*
\ipi Repent ye therefore, and be converted, (i.e. turn away from sin to the living God) that your sins may be blotted out.\vp(Acts 3:19)\vp*
\ipi Accept Jesus and sin no more, for God has appointed a day on which he will judge the world in righteousness, according to the man (Jesus Christ) whom he has appointed. Whereof he hath given assurance unto all men, in that he hath raised him from the dead.\vp(Acts 17:31)\vp*
\ipi For with the heart man believeth unto righteousness; and with the mouth confession is made unto salvation..\vp(Rom 10:10)\vp* Your prayer (a sincere conversation with God) should be like this.
\ipi Say aloud:
\ipi "Jesus, I am sorry for all my sins. Please forgive me, set me free and cleanse me completely. I accept you as my Savior, Lord and Lord of my life. Thank You for paying the price for me on the cross, dying and rising again on the third day."
